TypeSignature.Value: .class nested public auto ansi abstract sealed beforefieldinit Unicode/Script extends System.Object

Docs.summary: Static class containing the Unicode script tables.

remarks.para: There are static properties that can be used to fetch a specific category, or you can use the method in this class to retrieve the range table by its script name
